til run time, so it cannot be linked to a DLL import or export.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2492:  \n  \n```  \n// C2492.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \nclass C {  \npublic:  \n   char   ch;  \n};  \n  \n__declspec(dllexport) __declspec(thread) C c_1;   // C2492  \n__declspec(thread) C c_1;   // OK  \n```"}